{"tid":192913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敘利亞受化武攻擊小鎮再被空襲 至少十八死","createTime":"2017-04-09T02:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T04:43:47.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd4aa3c8b8d929e10e303ed953fd693caec2573","tid":192913,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"敘利亞西北部伊德利卜省一個小鎮，受到化學武器攻擊後，在周末再受到兩輪空襲。敘利亞一個人權監察組織表示，空襲造成最少十八人死亡，包括五名兒童，預計死傷數字仍會進一步上升。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，一架敘利亞軍直升機其中一個受空襲地點，南部一座被反對派控制的城市，投放炸彈，一直以來只有俄羅斯和敘利亞政府軍在有關地區執行任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=933716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D933716&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2a550362\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=933716</a>"},{"pid":"ed1826298315a6c1442c55f234662cd70ab1f306","tid":192913,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"証明美國佬射岩目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608127d77808f9354f3c43933109240d3df1051b","tid":192913,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"第2段又寫漏字<br />\n屌你老母依家啲記者真係"},{"pid":"78da5ca7e6c8681a7076d68066606cd95252525e","tid":192913,"uid":57741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第2段又寫漏字<br />\n屌你老母依家啲記者真係</blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇都覺得好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5d210df46483216162a18f63353b2df08dd996","tid":192913,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"巴沙爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}